{"tid":1501261,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【逆權運動】防暴警九龍灣開槍驅散 示威者疑遭橡膠子彈射傷左眼送院","createTime":"2019-08-24T10:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T10:35:30.000Z","uid":216555,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"17f21939145041f5ce0ac9d5764547a96c28abeb","tid":1501261,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hBCAP7N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhBCAP7N.jpg&h=a8835984&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsG6ck7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsG6ck7.png&h=19e124b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GOwNGet.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOwNGet.png&h=00ceb8a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n觀塘今午舉行遊行，警民再次發生衝突，警方再次施放催淚彈及開槍發射橡膠子彈、海綿彈、胡椒球等，混亂期間，一名於偉業街的男示威者疑似被橡膠子彈擊中左眼，血流披面，同時因吸入催淚彈感暈眩，他中槍後一度驚慌說：「我會唔會盲眼」、「我會唔會睇唔到嘢」。現場義務急救人員即時扶他離開及急救，救護車其後到場將示威者送院，暫時未知其傷勢如何。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【逆權運動】港大醫科生深圳過關受查半小時 強迫登入fb、IG刪相退組<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n8.31五周年民陣再集結<br />\n<br />\n日期：8月31日（星期六）<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集結，3時起步<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園遊行至中聯辦<br />\n註︰不反對通知書申請中"},{"pid":"2b64c1f023aa81171e9be52a2a9b0b2812d53349","tid":1501261,"uid":94180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:15:22.000Z","msg":"各手足小心！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501228</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n緊急 幫推thx！！！"},{"pid":"362a82fc58e09ca1815f373d7d0b5f6996daabe1","tid":1501261,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe2268b4c5253af104f3a27ee2efcad2d8ff526","tid":1501261,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:18:50.000Z","msg":"全民救港 全民勇武<br /